288
00:11:21,582 --> 00:11:22,781
Still don't believe me, huh?

289
00:11:24,781 --> 00:11:25,501
Yes,

290
00:11:26,302 --> 00:11:27,302
I believe

291
00:11:27,462 --> 00:11:28,102
what you said.

292
00:11:43,102 --> 00:11:43,982
I remember

293
00:11:44,422 --> 00:11:45,861
you had a distinctive wristband

294
00:11:46,901 --> 00:11:47,942
different from ours.

295
00:11:51,102 --> 00:11:51,621
Yes.

296
00:11:52,621 --> 00:11:53,621
That was specially made

297
00:11:53,741 --> 00:11:55,062
for us three brothers.

298
00:11:55,541 --> 00:11:56,582
But yours,

299
00:11:56,582 --> 00:11:58,182
and the one Ruoxi left you,

300
00:11:58,462 --> 00:12:00,021
were mass-produced later.

301
00:12:01,661 --> 00:12:04,182
Su Yunian, I know
what you're investigating.

302
00:12:05,102 --> 00:12:06,021
Let me say it again.

303
00:12:06,302 --> 00:12:06,982
It wasn't me.

304
00:12:07,422 --> 00:12:08,582
I'd never have killed Ruoxi.

305
00:12:08,942 --> 00:12:09,702
Do you understand?

306
00:12:12,182 --> 00:12:13,102
But,

307
00:12:13,422 --> 00:12:15,621
I hope if there's a chance,

308
00:12:15,621 --> 00:12:16,822
I can see that wristband.

309
00:12:17,302 --> 00:12:17,802
Can I,

310
00:12:17,982 --> 00:12:18,501
Mr. Tu?

311
00:12:18,781 --> 00:12:19,342
Yes.

312
00:12:20,222 --> 00:12:21,102
It's in my drawer.

313
00:12:21,582 --> 00:12:23,501
When the time comes,
I'll tell you everything.

314
00:12:24,021 --> 00:12:25,501
- Because what's involved...
- Okay.

315
00:12:26,741 --> 00:12:28,582
Since you're being sincere,

316
00:12:28,982 --> 00:12:30,062
let me mix you a drink.

317
00:12:30,861 --> 00:12:31,781
A Hint of Sorrow?

318
00:12:31,781 --> 00:12:32,781
Or Tangled Threads?

319
00:12:33,222 --> 00:12:35,381
Tonight, I'm with you till the end.

320
00:12:36,822 --> 00:12:37,462
Here?

321
00:12:38,582 --> 00:12:39,342
I've been prepared.

322
00:12:40,621 --> 00:12:41,302
Good.

323
00:12:42,141 --> 00:12:42,942
Drink till we drop.

324
00:12:43,342 --> 00:12:44,141
Drink till we drop.

325
00:12:55,021 --> 00:12:55,822
Feng.

326
00:12:56,462 --> 00:12:57,861
Long time no see, Lu.

327
00:12:59,261 --> 00:13:00,582
I specially prepared it for you.

328
00:13:02,182 --> 00:13:03,381
What era is this now?

329
00:13:03,381 --> 00:13:05,102
How did you find
this old-fashioned soda?

330
00:13:07,102 --> 00:13:08,422
In this world,

331
00:13:08,422 --> 00:13:10,021
as long as you invest time

332
00:13:10,021 --> 00:13:11,021
and effort,

333
00:13:11,741 --> 00:13:13,141
there's nothing you can't get.

334
00:13:13,141 --> 00:13:14,741
Your house is huge!

335
00:13:17,901 --> 00:13:18,541
Hurry.

336
00:13:18,781 --> 00:13:20,021
I saved a soda just for you.

337
00:13:27,501 --> 00:13:28,621
You're the best, Feng.

338
00:13:28,621 --> 00:13:29,901
This is my favorite.

339
00:13:30,141 --> 00:13:30,901
Don't worry.

340
00:13:31,062 --> 00:13:33,021
From now on, if I have a sip,

341
00:13:33,222 --> 00:13:34,422
you'll have one too.

342
00:13:34,482 --> 00:13:34,982
Feng,

343
00:13:34,982 --> 00:13:36,062
you're so nice to me.

344
00:13:36,102 --> 00:13:38,102
From now on, you're my real big brother.

345
00:13:39,182 --> 00:13:39,982
Drink up.

346
00:13:41,222 --> 00:13:43,982
I'll always be your brother.

347
00:13:44,781 --> 00:13:46,261
If I have a sip,

348
00:13:46,661 --> 00:13:47,781
you'll have one too.

349
00:13:48,901 --> 00:13:49,501
Sit.

350
00:13:58,541 --> 00:14:00,942
Tangled Threads and A Hint of Sorrow,

351
00:14:01,541 --> 00:14:03,062
which one would you like first?

352
00:14:12,021 --> 00:14:13,062
Tangled Threads.

353
00:14:13,661 --> 00:14:14,582
A Hint of Sorrow.

354
00:14:14,781 --> 00:14:16,342
Ruoxi used this poem

355
00:14:16,422 --> 00:14:17,982
to name these two drinks.

356
00:14:18,901 --> 00:14:19,822
Look back now,

357
00:14:20,342 --> 00:14:21,942
and it feels a bit prophetic.

358
00:14:24,741 --> 00:14:25,422
I know

359
00:14:26,982 --> 00:14:27,982
even if you believe me,

360
00:14:29,141 --> 00:14:29,982
you won't forgive me.

361
00:14:30,861 --> 00:14:31,582
After all,

362
00:14:31,982 --> 00:14:33,102
I failed to protect Ruoxi.

363
00:14:36,582 --> 00:14:37,422
Tell me

364
00:14:38,342 --> 00:14:39,541
about you and Ruoxi.

365
00:14:40,822 --> 00:14:41,702
With so many stories,

366
00:14:42,141 --> 00:14:43,302
where to begin?

367
00:14:49,342 --> 00:14:50,661
(From: Captain Liu of Security Dept.)
(Still can't reach Mr. Zhao.)

368
00:14:50,781 --> 00:14:52,222
(We've checked all his usual spots.)

369
00:14:53,982 --> 00:14:54,781
Anywhere.

370
00:14:55,222 --> 00:14:56,062
I want to hear it.

371
00:14:56,741 --> 00:14:57,582
(To: Captain Liu of Security Dept.)
(Keep looking.)

372
00:14:57,661 --> 00:14:58,582
(You must find him.)

373
00:15:01,302 --> 00:15:02,062
Then,

374
00:15:02,621 --> 00:15:03,982
let's start with her dream.

375
00:15:04,942 --> 00:15:05,861
For that dream,

376
00:15:06,741 --> 00:15:07,901
she truly gave so much.

377
00:15:10,901 --> 00:15:11,582
Begin.

378
00:15:12,381 --> 00:15:12,982
Tonight,

379
00:15:13,261 --> 00:15:14,062
drinks are on me.

380
00:15:17,102 --> 00:15:17,741
Mr. Tu,

381
00:15:17,982 --> 00:15:18,621
a toast to you.

382
00:15:42,528 --> 00:15:46,202
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

383
00:15:46,501 --> 00:15:49,692
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

384
00:15:51,328 --> 00:15:55,145
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

385
00:15:55,694 --> 00:15:58,493
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

386
00:15:59,964 --> 00:16:03,694
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

387
00:16:03,918 --> 00:16:07,415
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

388
00:16:08,814 --> 00:16:12,501
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

389
00:16:13,139 --> 00:16:18,254
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

390
00:16:18,958 --> 00:16:23,092
♪I feel guilty♪

391
00:16:23,662 --> 00:16:27,406
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

392
00:16:28,270 --> 00:16:31,713
♪Even in tears♪

393
00:16:32,462 --> 00:16:36,376
♪It doesn't matter♪

394
00:16:36,558 --> 00:16:40,381
♪We embrace in dreams♪

395
00:16:41,230 --> 00:16:44,668
♪I let down all my defenses♪

396
00:16:45,902 --> 00:16:49,265
♪Though the story has its end♪

397
00:16:50,030 --> 00:16:57,504
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
